IN THE NORTH END.

02:50.770 --> 02:54.467
HER BODY, SANS HEAD,
WAS LEFI' ON AN OLD COUCH
BY THE CURB.

02:54.500 --> 02:56.263
THE NORTH END
AND ROXBURY

