MUST HAVE USED A VAN
OR OTHER VEHICLE

03:10.620 --> 03:11.917
TO TRANSPORT THE BODIES.

03:11.950 --> 03:15.408
NOT TO BE INDELICATE,
BUT ANY SIGN OF THE HEADS?

03:15.460 --> 03:16.256
NO, NOTHING YET.

03:16.290 --> 03:17.780
