HAVING A FIELD DAY.

03:17.830 --> 03:20.219
OH, YOU COULD SAY THAT.

03:21.500 --> 03:24.560
OH, WELL,
NOT NEARLY AS CLEVER

03:24.600 --> 03:26.261
AS THAT INFAMOUS
"NEW YORK POST" HEADLINE:

03:26.300 --> 03:27.836
"HEADLESS BODY
IN TOPLESS BAR."

03:27.870 --> 03:29.428
HE DUMPED THE BODIES
IN PUBLIC,

03:29.470 --> 03:30.937
