BETWEEN THEM, I'M NOT SEEING IT.

05:40.570 --> 05:43.607
WELL, THE FIRST VICTIM,
LILY CHANG, WAS A CHEMISTRY
MAJOR AT M.I.T.

05:43.640 --> 05:46.632
