05:57.020 --> 05:58.578
TO SEND A MESSAGE
OR A WARNING.

05:58.620 --> 06:00.383
HISTORICALLY IT'S BEEN
USED FOR THAT PURPOSE,

06:00.420 --> 06:01.682
STARTING WITH THE ANCIENT
GREEKS AND ROMANS.

06:01.720 --> 06:04.052
IN 11th CENTURY ENGLAND
BEHEADING BY SWORD

06:04.090 --> 06:05.785
