WILLIAM THE CONQUEROR.

06:05.830 --> 06:07.559
AND OF COURSE THOUSANDS
OF PEOPLE WERE BEHEADED

06:07.600 --> 06:08.726
DURING THE FRENCH
REVOLUTION,

06:08.760 --> 06:10.398
INCLUDING LOUIS XVI
AND MARIE ANTOINETTE.

06:10.430 --> 06:12.762
COULD THE BE THE WORK OF
A TERRORIST CELL ON U.S. SOIL?

06:12.800 --> 06:14.563
