06:41.660 --> 06:43.594
ON A BENCH
IN BOSTON COMMON.

06:43.630 --> 06:45.063
THE COMMONS IS RIGHT
IN THE HEART OF DOWNTOWN.

06:45.100 --> 06:47.136
