PICKED A MORE PUBLIC PLACE.

06:47.170 --> 06:48.467
LILY CHANG WAS KILLED
A WEEK AGO,

06:48.500 --> 06:49.728
DENISE WAGNER
TWO DAYS AGO,

06:49.770 --> 06:50.907
AND NOW AMY GIBB.

06:50.940 --> 06:52.805
