WE NEED TO KNOW
WHO THOSE VICTIMS
SPOKE TO LAST.

12:53.300 --> 12:54.858
COPY THAT.

12:54.900 --> 12:56.333
AMY WORKED
AT THE SEAPORT.
THAT'S IN SOUTHIE.

12:56.370 --> 12:58.258
SO WAS THE SCHOOL
WHERE LILY TUTORED

12:58.310 --> 13:00.835
AND THE CONVENTION
CENTER WHERE DENISE
ATTENDED A SEMINAR.

13:00.880 --> 13:03.007
IT COULD BE THE NEIGHBORHOOD
THAT'S IMPORTANT TO HIM.

13:03.050 --> 13:05.143
YOU KNOW, SOUTHIE'S STILL
PREDOMINANTLY WORKING-CLASS
IRISH-AMERICAN.

13:05.180 --> 13:07.273
HOWEVER, LONG-TIME RESIDENTS
THERE ARE STRUGGLING
TO HOLD ON

13:07.320 --> 13:10.244
TO THEIR HOMES AND
TRADITIONS IN THE FACE
OF GENTRIFICATION.

13:10.290 --> 13:13.987
FANCY WORD FOR ORGANIC
GROCERY STORES, CONDOS,
AND JUICE BARS.

13:14.020 --> 13:15.385
AMY TOOK THE T
ABOUT ABOUT MIDNIGHT.

13:15.420 --> 13:16.978
THE UNSUB COULD HAVE
FOLLOWED HER HOME.

13:17.030 --> 13:18.827
IF LILY AND DENISE
ALSO TOOK THE TRAIN,

13:18.860 --> 13:20.293
MAYBE THAT'S WHERE
HE GRABBED THEM.

13:20.330 --> 13:23.265
HE USED A TASER.
TOO RISKY IN THE SUBWAY.

13:23.300 --> 13:25.393
AMY COULDN'T HAVE TAKEN
THE T AT THAT TIME.
SERVICE WAS SHUT DOWN.

13:25.430 --> 13:28.399
BUT ARTHUR GIBB SAID
HE SPOKE TO HER THERE.
GARCIA?

13:28.440 --> 13:32.137
AND HE DID. GPS CONFIRMS
THAT AMY WAS AT THE STATION.

13:32.170 --> 13:33.876
BUT DETECTIVE LAWLOR
IS CORRECT.

13:33.910 --> 13:35.377
RIGHT Al-TER AMY ARRIVED,

13:35.410 --> 13:38.504
SERVICE ON THAT LINE
WAS DISRUPTED
DUE TO A TRACK FIRE.

13:38.550 --> 13:40.017
WHERE DID AMY GO
AI-TER THAT?

13:40.050 --> 13:42.041
I HAVE HER MOVING AWAY
FROM THE STATION,

13:42.080 --> 13:44.014
ARRIVING AT HER HOUSE
20 MINUTES LATER.

13:44.050 --> 13:45.142
THAT'S WHEN THE SIGNAL DIES.

13:45.190 --> 13:46.441
MAYBE SHE TOOK
THE BUS HOME?

13:46.490 --> 13:48.879
IT WOULD HAVE TAKEN HER
LONGER THAN 20 MINUTES.

13:48.920 --> 13:50.888
GARCIA, DID SHE CALL
A TAXI OR CAR SERVICE?

13:50.930 --> 13:54.388
SHE DID. SHE ORDERED A CAR
FROM A RIDE-SHARE COMPANY
CALLED ZIMMER,

13:54.430 --> 13:56.352
BUT SHE CANCELED IT
MINUTES LATER.

13:56.400 --> 13:59.995
SO HOW DID AMY GET HOME?

14:09.010 --> 14:11.046
WAIT, WAIT. HEY, HEY, HEY!

14:14.980 --> 14:17.380
LISTEN, I'LL PAY CASH
AND DOUBLE THE TIP

14:17.420 --> 14:20.389
IF YOU DRIVE ME
TO DORCHESTER.
NAME YOUR PRICE.

14:20.420 --> 14:24.982
THE CAR I ORDERED
IS 10 MINUTES AWAY
AND I GOTTA GET HOME.

14:25.030 --> 14:27.021
GET IN.

14:27.060 --> 14:28.527
YES!

14:35.000 --> 14:39.061
MAN, YOU JUST SAVED MY LIFE.
YOU HAVE NO IDEA.

14:41.010 --> 14:43.001
AMY GIBB'S FATHER
SAID SHE WAS DEPRESSED

14:43.050 --> 14:44.972
AND A LITTLE LOST
AI-TER HER MOTHER DIED,

14:45.010 --> 14:46.375
BUT WHAT HE DIDN'T MENTION
IS THAT A MONTH AGO

14:46.410 --> 14:48.048
SHE GOT CAUGHT
FOR SHOPLII-TING.

14:48.080 --> 14:49.308
RESEARCH HAS SHOWN
A DIRECT CORRELATION

14:49.350 --> 14:50.647
BETWEEN SHOPLII-TING
AND DEPRESSION.

14:50.690 --> 14:54.319
IT'S OI-TEN A REACTION
TO SOME KIND OF LOSS
OR NEED TO FILL A VOID.

14:54.360 --> 14:56.112
ALL RIGHT, WELL,
THE SECOND VICTIM,

14:56.160 --> 14:58.628
DENISE WAGNER, JUST
HAD HER ASSETS FROZEN
BY THE S.E.C.

14:58.660 --> 15:00.958
DUE TO ALLEGATIONS
OF INSIDER TRADING.

15:01.000 --> 15:03.298
ANYTHING HINKY
ON THE FIRST VICTIM?

15:03.330 --> 15:04.524
LILY CHANG'S TRANSCRIPTS
SHOW THAT SHE WAS

15:04.570 --> 15:07.494
ON ACADEMIC PROBATION
FROM M.I.T. AND CLOSE
TO FLUNKING OUT.

15:07.540 --> 15:09.633
WELL, I TAKE BACK WHAT I SAID
ABOUT NOT SEEING A CONNECTION

15:09.670 --> 15:12.639
BETWEEN THE VICTIMS.
ALL 3 WERE INVOLVED
IN UNETHICAL SITUATIONS

15:12.670 --> 15:14.035
THEY PROBABLY
WEREN'T PROUD OF.

15:14.080 --> 15:15.934
[BEEP]
HELLO, G-MEN AND G-WOMAN.

15:15.980 --> 15:17.299
HEY, WHAT UP, BABY GIRL?

15:17.350 --> 15:20.012
OK, I HAVE BEEN DOING
RESEARCH ON SUPER-SHARP

15:20.050 --> 15:21.244
POSSIBLE
HEAD-CHOPPING WEAPONRY.

15:21.280 --> 15:23.043
WHAT'D YOU FIND?

15:23.090 --> 15:25.149
[SIGHS] THERE ARE SO MANY
WAYS TO SLICE AND DICE.

15:25.190 --> 15:27.158
AXES, MACHETES, KNIVES, SWORDS.

15:27.190 --> 15:30.079
DO YOU KNOW THERE'S
A SWORD FROM ASIA
CALLED THE KATANA?

15:30.130 --> 15:31.984
IT CAN SLICE A PERSON
IN HALF.
WHO WOULD NEED THAT?

15:32.030 --> 15:34.157
COULD BE WHAT
THE UNSUB'S USING.

15:34.200 --> 15:35.952
WELL, IN THE LAST 6 MONTHS,
IN BOSTON,

15:36.000 --> 15:39.128
THERE HAVE BEEN 20 SWORDS
SOLD, BOTH REAL AND REPLICAS,

15:39.170 --> 15:40.990
MOSTLY TO BUYERS WHO JUST
WANTED TO ADD THEM

15:41.040 --> 15:42.268
TO THEIR PRIVATE COLLECTIONS.

15:42.300 --> 15:43.631
WELL, WHO ELSE
BOUGHT THEM?

15:43.670 --> 15:46.059
UH, PEOPLE LIKE MOI
WHO GO TO RENAISSANCE FAIRS

15:48.340 --> 15:50.171
DON'T JUDGE ME.

15:50.210 --> 15:52.041
I'M NOT, BUT WE'RE GONNA
NEED TO TALK TO EVERYONE,

15:52.080 --> 15:53.274
SO SEND US THE INFORMATION.

15:53.320 --> 15:55.174
DONE AND DONE
AND DONE AND DONE.

15:55.220 --> 15:57.211
YOU KNOW, THE UNSUB'S
METHOD OF KILLING

15:57.250 --> 15:59.184
HAS CERTAINLY EVOLVED
SINCE THE FIRST KILL,

15:59.220 --> 16:02.109
BUT I DON'T THINK HE'S USING
ANY OF THE WEAPONS
THAT GARCIA FOUND.

16:02.160 --> 16:04.253
WHAT ABOUT THE KATANA?
THAT CAN SEVER A NECK
WITH PRECISION.

16:04.290 --> 16:08.021
IT WOULD GIVE HIM
THE EFFICIENCY AND
ACCURACY WE'VE SEEN, BUT...

16:08.060 --> 16:09.652
WHAT? WHAT ARE
YOU THINKING?

16:09.700 --> 16:11.395
DISPLAYING THE BODIES
IN PUBLIC

16:11.430 --> 16:13.068
SEEMS TO BE WHAT'S
IMPORTANT TO THE UNSUB.

16:13.100 --> 16:15.239
HE WANTS TO MAKE AN EXAMPLE
OUT OF HIS VICTIMS,

16:15.270 --> 16:18.159
WHICH IS WHY I THINK
HE'S USING A GUILLOTINE.

16:18.210 --> 16:19.666
YOU'RE SERIOUS.

16:19.710 --> 16:22.076
GUILLOTINES WERE ONCE
CONSIDERED INSTRUMENTS
OF JUSTICE.

16:22.110 --> 16:23.543
EXECUTIONS WERE PUBLIC EVENTS.

16:23.580 --> 16:26.378
CROWDS WOULD COME AND LITERALLY
BRING PICNIC BASKETS.

16:26.410 --> 16:28.116
PARENTS WOULD BRING
THEIR KIDS.

16:28.150 --> 16:30.186
NOW, HE CAN'T KILL
IN TODAY'S TOWN SQUARE,

16:30.220 --> 16:31.482
SO HE'S DOING
THE NEXT BEST THING.

16:31.520 --> 16:34.011
HE'S DUMPING THE BODIES
FOR THE PUBLIC TO FIND.

16:34.060 --> 16:36.051
OK, GUILLOTINES
AREN'T EXACTLY

16:36.090 --> 16:38.422
SOMETHING YOU SEE
BEING SOLD ON AMAZON
EVERY DAY.

16:38.460 --> 16:40.098
NO, BUT IT WOULD BE
SO EASY TO MAKE ONE.

16:40.130 --> 16:41.757
ALL YOU NEED IS WOOD,
ROPE, PULLEYS,
AND SHEET METAL

16:41.800 --> 16:44.268
FROM THE LOCAL
HARDWARE STORE.

16:46.270 --> 16:49.194
NO, I'M FINE, REALLY.

16:49.240 --> 16:51.435
SOME OUT OF THE WAY HOTEL
IN SOUTHIE.

16:51.470 --> 16:53.779
MY WIFE THINKS
I WAS MEETING A CLIENT
AI-TER WORK.

16:53.810 --> 16:59.168
NO, I DON'T THINK
SHE SUSPECTS.

16:59.210 --> 17:02.816
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT,
CURTIS, IT WON'T.

17:02.850 --> 17:05.546
LISTEN, I GOTTA GO.

17:05.590 --> 17:09.287
HEY, THIS ISN'T THE WAY
TO DORCHESTER.

17:11.430 --> 17:13.421
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

17:13.460 --> 17:15.121
WHY ARE WE STOPPING?

17:15.160 --> 17:16.229
HEY, WHERE THE HELL ARE WE?

17:16.260 --> 17:17.818
AAH! AAH!

17:17.870 --> 17:19.462
AAH!

17:24.110 --> 17:25.099
LIKE AMY GIBB,
THE FIRST TWO VICTIMS

17:25.140 --> 17:27.131
HAD CALLED FOR RIDE-SHARE
CARS AND THEN CANCELED.

17:27.180 --> 17:28.431
TO ME, THIS WHOLE
RIDE-SHARE THING'S

17:28.480 --> 17:31.301
NOT MUCH DIFFERENT
THAN HITCHHIKING,

17:31.350 --> 17:33.079
EXCEPT YOU GOTTA PAY.

17:33.120 --> 17:34.576
I GET THE APPEAL.
IT'S QUICK AND EASY.

17:34.620 --> 17:36.838
YOU JUST HAVE TO ENTER
YOUR LOCATION
VIA SMARTPHONE.

17:36.880 --> 17:39.246
RIGHT. AND THEN SOME
RANDOM CAR PULLS UP
AND YOU HOP IN.

17:39.290 --> 17:40.609
THAT SOUNDS SAFE.

17:40.660 --> 17:41.854
WELL, RIDERS ARE SENT
THE DRIVER'S NAME,

17:41.890 --> 17:45.189
PHOTO, LICENSE PLATE
NUMBER. THEY KNOW
WHO'S PICKING THEM UP.

17:45.230 --> 17:46.424
MAYBE THE VICTIMS
DIDN'T WANT TO WAIT

17:46.460 --> 17:48.724
FOR THEIR RIDE-SHARE
CARS TO ARRIVE
AND HAILED A TAXI INSTEAD.

17:48.760 --> 17:51.194
AND IF THE CABBIE
HAD A JAMMER,
THAT WOULD EXPLAIN

17:51.230 --> 17:52.561
WHY THE VICTIMS'
PHONE SIGNALS DIED.

17:52.600 --> 17:55.489
HE COULD BLITZ ATTACK THEM
IN THE CAB AND THEN
DISABLE THEIR PHONES.

17:55.540 --> 17:57.861
EXCEPT AMY WAS
AT HER FRONT DOOR WHEN
HER CELL SIGNAL DIED.

17:57.910 --> 18:01.107
TAXI DRIVERS DON'T
USUALLY ESCORT PASSENGERS
TO THEIR DOOR.

18:01.140 --> 18:02.778
MAYBE THIS ONE DID FOR AMY.

18:02.810 --> 18:04.869
JJ: WALKING PASSENGERS
TO THEIR DOOR

18:04.910 --> 18:06.741
FEELS MORE LIKE SOMETHING
A RIDE-SHARE DRIVER WOULD DO

18:06.780 --> 18:08.270
IN HOPES OF GETTING
A POSITIVE REVIEW.

18:08.320 --> 18:09.810
Lewis: LET'S GO FIND OUT.

18:13.160 --> 18:16.254
ZIMMER DRIVERS GO THROUGH
RIGOROUS BACKGROUND CHECKS.

18:16.290 --> 18:18.429
DOES THAT INCLUDE
FINGERPRINT-BASED
BACKGROUND CHECKS

18:18.460 --> 18:19.757
THROUGH THE DOJ
AND FBI SYSTEMS

18:19.790 --> 18:21.758
LIKE TAXI COMPANIES
ARE REQUIRED TO DO?

18:21.800 --> 18:22.721
NO.

18:22.760 --> 18:24.899
WHAT ABOUT THE NATIONAL
SEX OFFENDER DATABASE?

18:24.930 --> 18:27.831
WE LEAD THE INDUSTRY
WITH OUR SCREENING PROCESS.

18:27.870 --> 18:29.895
WE'RE EVEN ABOUT
TO INTRODUCE AN APP
FOR CHILDREN

18:29.940 --> 18:31.805
WHOSE PARENTS ARE
TOO BUSY TO SHUTTLE
THEM AROUND.

18:31.840 --> 18:34.536
HOW DO YOU KNOW
WHEN YOU HAVE
A PROBLEM DRIVER?

18:34.580 --> 18:36.275
NEGATIVE CUSTOMER REVIEWS.

18:36.310 --> 18:38.278
TOO MANY AND YOUR ACCOUNT
IS SUSPENDED

18:38.310 --> 18:40.312
OR PERMANENTLY DEACTIVATED.

18:40.350 --> 18:43.478
BUT ZIMMER ISN'T RESPONSIBLE
FOR THE CONDUCT
OF ITS DRIVERS.

18:43.520 --> 18:45.613
AND WHY IS THAT?

18:45.650 --> 18:47.618
THEY'RE INDEPENDENT
CONTRACTORS.

18:47.660 --> 18:51.323
SO IF A DRIVER
WERE TO KIDNAP ME
OR GET DRUNK

18:51.360 --> 18:54.158
AND DRIVE OFF A BRIDGE
WITH ME SITTING
RIGHT NEXT TO HIM,

18:54.200 --> 18:56.259
YOU'RE CLAIMING
ZIMMER'S NOT RESPONSIBLE.

18:56.300 --> 18:58.666
A BIT DRAMATIC, BUT TRUE.

18:58.700 --> 19:01.498
ZIMMER IS MERELY
A TECHNOLOGY PLATFORM

19:01.540 --> 19:04.202
THAT MATCHES WILLING
DRIVERS AND PASSENGERS.

19:04.240 --> 19:06.936
WHAT IF SOMEONE WANTS TO HACK
YOUR RIDE-SHARE APP?

19:06.970 --> 19:09.177
THEY COULD BE PICKING UP
PASSENGERS

19:09.210 --> 19:11.474
BEFORE THEIR ACTUAL DRIVERS
EVER ARRIVE.

19:12.750 --> 19:14.843
YOUR ZIMMER APP WAS HACKED.

19:14.880 --> 19:17.815
WE HAD SOME TROUBLE
RECENTLY.

19:17.850 --> 19:19.386
WHEN?

19:20.390 --> 19:21.857
LAST WEEK.

19:21.890 --> 19:24.222
BUT OUR CYBER-SECURITY
TEAM WAS ABLE TO TRACE IT

19:24.260 --> 19:27.798
TO A RIVAL COMPANY
TRYING TO POACH
OUR CUSTOMER BASE.

19:45.610 --> 19:47.544
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

19:47.580 --> 19:50.811
OW! [MOANING]

19:53.260 --> 19:55.455
OF ALL THE CARS
YOU COULD HAVE GOT INTO,

19:55.490 --> 19:56.957
YOU GOT INTO MINE.

19:56.990 --> 20:00.892
SOME MIGHT SAY
THAT LUCK OR FATE
BROUGHT US TOGETHER.

20:03.470 --> 20:07.793
[SIGH] I LIKE TO THINK
THAT IT WAS DIVINE INTERVENTION.

20:14.510 --> 20:16.603
IT'S TIME WE GET STARTED.

20:20.650 --> 20:22.868
OH, NO, NO.

20:22.920 --> 20:24.581
OH, NO, NO, NO.

20:24.620 --> 20:26.918
IF THE UNSUB'S NOT HACKING
RIDE-SHARE APPS,

20:26.950 --> 20:29.612
THEN WHAT'S TO STOP HIM
FROM SIMPLY POSING
AS A DRIVER?

20:29.660 --> 20:31.924
I MEAN, ALL HE'D HAVE
TO DO IS THROW A DECAL
ON A CAR WINDOW

20:31.960 --> 20:33.825
AND CRUISE AROUND
TARGET-RICH ENVIRONMENTS

20:33.860 --> 20:35.623
LIKE RESTAURANTS,
CLUBS, AND BARS.

20:35.660 --> 20:37.628
YEAH, HE COULD JUST
PRETEND THERE WAS
A PROBLEM WITH THE APP

20:37.670 --> 20:39.467
AND THEN OFFER A DISCOUNT
IF THE RIDER PAYS CASH

20:39.500 --> 20:40.899
AND CANCELS THE CAR
THEY ALREADY ORDERED.

20:40.940 --> 20:43.329
MM-HMM.

20:43.370 --> 20:44.337
I LOVE YA!

20:44.370 --> 20:45.769
HEY, BABY GIRL, LISTEN.

20:45.810 --> 20:47.277
I NEED YOU TO LOOK
AT JOB APPLICATIONS

20:47.310 --> 20:48.800
SUBMITTED BY
RIDE-SHARE DRIVERS.

20:48.840 --> 20:51.775
THAT IS A TALL ORDER,
MY FAVORITE FLAVOR
OF HOT CHOCOLATE.

20:51.810 --> 20:53.619
AND YOU'LL HAVE TO GIVE ME
UN POQUITO MAS.

20:53.650 --> 20:55.777
THOUSANDS OF PEOPLE APPLY
FOR THOSE JOBS EVERY DAY.

20:55.820 --> 20:58.288
WELL, FIND LOCAL DRIVERS
WHO WERE REJECTED.

20:58.320 --> 20:59.912
YEAH, ALSO CHECK FOR
CURRENT RIDE-SHARE
DRIVERS IN THE AREA

20:59.950 --> 21:03.920
WITH CRIMINAL HISTORIES
THAT DATE BACK PRIOR
TO 7 YEARS AGO.

21:03.960 --> 21:06.929
RIGHT. BECAUSE BACKGROUND
CHECKS OI-TEN DON'T GO
THAT FAR BACK.

21:06.960 --> 21:08.689
OK, I'LL CATCH YOU
ON THE FLIPSIDE.

21:08.730 --> 21:11.995
WELL, IT'S TIME
TO GIVE THE PROFILE.

21:12.030 --> 21:14.863
THE UNSUB WE'RE LOOKING FOR
MAY BE A RIDE-SHARE DRIVER

21:14.900 --> 21:18.563
OR POSING AS ONE
AND IS USING THAT SERVICE
TO HUNT FOR HIS VICTIMS.

21:18.610 --> 21:19.963
HE APPEARS
NON-THREATENING,

21:20.010 --> 21:22.308
WHICH ALLOWS HIM
TO GET CLOSE
TO HIS VICTIMS.

21:22.340 --> 21:23.944
THE SOPHISTICATED
NATURE OF HIS PLANNING

21:23.980 --> 21:26.073
SUGGESTS HE'S IN HIS
LATE 305 OR EARLY 40$.

21:26.110 --> 21:27.941
WE THINK HE'S
AN INJUSTICE COLLECTOR,

21:27.980 --> 21:31.643
UPSET BY WHAT HE CONSIDERS
TO BE THE UNFAIRNESS
OF HIS LIFE.

21:31.690 --> 21:32.941
HE HOLDS ON TO GRUDGES,

21:32.990 --> 21:35.686
AND HE MAGNIFIES SLIGHTS
WAY OUT OF PROPORTION.

21:35.720 --> 21:38.757
HIS HYPERSENSITIVITY
COULD BE THE RESULT
OF PARANOIA

21:38.790 --> 21:40.326
OR DRUG-INDUCED PSYCHOSIS.

21:40.360 --> 21:42.499
RIDE-SHARE COMPANIES
USE SOFTWARE AND PHONE APPS

21:42.530 --> 21:44.669
TO TRACK THE DRIVERS
AND CUSTOMERS.

21:44.700 --> 21:46.497
COULD HE BE HACKING
THEIR SYSTEMS?

21:46.530 --> 21:48.839
WE'VE CHECKED EVERY RIDE-SHARE
COMPANY OPERATING IN BOSTON.

21:48.870 --> 21:50.098
THERE'S NO EVIDENCE OF THAT.

21:50.140 --> 21:52.005
HOWEVER, HE MAY BE GETTING
AROUND THE SOFTWARE

21:52.040 --> 21:54.531
BY PICKING HIS VICTIMS
OFF THE APP,

21:54.580 --> 21:56.070
SIMILAR TO WHEN
CONVENTIONAL TAXI DRIVERS

21:56.110 --> 21:57.577
GO OFF THE METER.

21:57.610 --> 21:59.407
EVEN THE MOST MINOR INSULT

21:59.450 --> 22:02.544
COULD CAUSE HIM TO FLY INTO
A MURDEROUS RAGE.

22:02.580 --> 22:04.081
Lewis: HE COULD ALSO
HAVE BEEN RAISED IN A HOME

22:04.120 --> 22:05.883
WHERE HE WAS EXCESSIVELY
DISCIPLINED.

22:05.920 --> 22:06.784
AAH!

22:06.820 --> 22:08.981
JJ: THE ACT OF STRIKING
HIS VICTIMS' HANDS

22:09.020 --> 22:10.681
MAY BE PART
OF THEIR PUNISHMENT.

22:10.730 --> 22:12.880
Rossi: AND THE BEHEADING
PROBABLY GIVES HIM THE POWER

22:12.930 --> 22:15.421
AND CONTROL
HE FEELS HE LACKS.

22:15.460 --> 22:17.564
THE PUBLIC IS ADVISED
TO TRAVEL IN PAIRS OR GROUPS

22:17.600 --> 22:19.659
AND TO USE PUBLIC
TRANSPORTATION
WHEN POSSIBLE.

22:19.700 --> 22:21.998
IF USING A TAXI,
PLEASE CALL THE COMPANY

22:22.040 --> 22:23.962
TO ORDER ONE IN LIEU OF
HAILING ONE IN THE STREET.

22:24.010 --> 22:25.034
AND IF YOU'RE A RIDE-SHARE
CUSTOMER,

22:25.070 --> 22:26.537
MAKE SURE THE CAR
THAT PICKS YOU UP

22:26.570 --> 22:27.935
IS THE ONE
THAT YOU RESERVED

22:27.980 --> 22:29.868
AND THE DRIVER
MATCHES THE PHOTO
THAT WAS SENT TO YOU.

22:29.910 --> 22:31.502
IF HE'S UPSET ABOUT CHANGES
IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD,

22:31.550 --> 22:33.916
HE MIGHT CONSIDER
OUTSIDERS TO BE THE ENEMY

22:33.950 --> 22:36.874
AND HIS FORM OF PUNISHMENT
IS DECAPITATION.

22:36.920 --> 22:38.888
THANK YOU.

22:38.920 --> 22:41.013
AGENTS, THERE'S A WOMAN HERE,

22:41.060 --> 22:43.881
SHE'S CONVINCED THAT HER
HUSBAND'S BEEN KIDNAPPED
BY THE KILLER.

22:43.930 --> 22:47.081
UP TO NOW, THE UNSUB'S
ONLY BEEN ABDUCTING
AND BEHEADING WOMEN.

22:47.130 --> 22:48.950
SHE'S BEING
PRETTY INSISTENT.

22:49.000 --> 22:50.865
YOU'LL PROBABLY GET
A LOT MORE LIKE HER
COMING IN HERE.

22:50.900 --> 22:54.028
SHE ALSO MENTIONED
HER HUSBAND'S A FREQUENT
USER OF RIDE-SHARE.

22:54.070 --> 22:55.094
JJ, LEWIS, CHECK IT OUT.

23:02.110 --> 23:04.078
HE'S GONNA
CHOP OFF HIS HEAD!

23:04.110 --> 23:06.840
I SAW THE NEWS.
I KNOW THAT THE BEHEADER
HAS MY HUSBAND.

23:06.880 --> 23:09.212
MRS. SIMMONS,
PLEASE HAVE A SEAT.

23:13.090 --> 23:15.115
WILL YOU TELL ME
WHY YOU THINK THIS?

23:15.160 --> 23:17.014
ANTHONY DIDN'T COME HOME
LAST NIGHT.

23:17.060 --> 23:18.152
HE'S NEVER NOT COME HOME

23:18.190 --> 23:20.124
IN THE 10 YEARS
THAT WE'VE BEEN MARRIED.

23:20.160 --> 23:23.049
OK, WHEN DID YOU LAST
SPEAK WITH HIM?

23:23.100 --> 23:25.864
YESTERDAY AFTERNOON.
UM, HE SAID THAT
HE HAD A CLIENT DINNER

23:25.900 --> 23:29.063
AND THAT HE'D BE HOME LATE.
BUT HE NEVER CAME HOME.

23:29.100 --> 23:32.831
YOU TOLD THE POLICE
THAT YOUR HUSBAND USED
RIDE-SHARE SERVICES?

23:32.870 --> 23:36.806
YES. ALL THE TIME.
