WITH A NUTCASE

23:55.500 --> 23:57.092
OR IS THE WIFE
ONTO SOMETHING?

23:57.130 --> 23:59.018
I'M HOPING GARCIA
CAN TELL US.

23:59.070 --> 24:01.038
GARCIA'S THE NAM E,
SERVICE THE GAME.

24:01.070 --> 24:04.107
HI, I'M LOOKING
FOR INFORMATION
ON AN ANTHONY SIMMONS.

24:04.140 --> 24:05.209
