WITH A CLIENT IN CHINATOWN
LAST NIGHT.

24:11.850 --> 24:14.114
ANYTHING TO SHOW HE WAS THERE?

24:14.150 --> 24:15.913
NO. I DON'T THINK
HE WAS DOING THAT.

24:15.950 --> 24:18.248
THERE ARE NO CREDIT CARD
RECORDS OF ANY BARS
OR RESTAURANTS

24:18.290 --> 24:19.939
IN CHINATOWN FOR HIM.

24:19.990 --> 24:22.151
WAS HE ANYWHERE
NEAR SOUTHIE?

24:22.190 --> 24:24.681
OH, HE WAS ALL OVER THAT
LIKE A CHEAP POLY-RAYON
BLEND SUIT.

24:24.730 --> 24:27.119
