TO A HOTEL CALLED THE MARQUEE.

24:27.160 --> 24:28.957
HE ORDERED ROOM SERVICE
FOR TWO--

24:29.000 --> 24:30.661
SHRIMP COCKTAIL, STEAK DIANE,
CREME BRULEE,

24:30.700 --> 24:33.260
3 BOTTLES OF CABERNET,
AND HE ALSO ORDERED

24:33.300 --> 24:36.497
AN IN-ROOM ADULT
ENTERTAINMENT MOVIE
ON PAY-PER-VIEW.

24:36.540 --> 24:39.100
I DON'T THINK HE'LL
BE ABLE TO PUT THAT
ON HIS EXPENSE ACCOUNT.

24:39.140 --> 24:41.176
DID HE USE
A RIDE-SHARE SERVICE?

24:41.210 --> 24:42.973
YEAH. HE USED A PLACE
CALLED VOYAGE

24:43.010 --> 24:44.238
FROM DOWNTOWN BOSTON
TO THE HOTEL.

24:44.280 --> 24:46.077
WHAT TIME DID HE CHECK OUT
THIS MORNING?

24:46.110 --> 24:47.839
HE DIDN'T. HE CHECKED OUT
THE SAME NIGHT

24:47.880 --> 24:49.711
AND HE ORDERED A ZIMMER CAR
TO DORCHESTER.

24:49.750 --> 24:51.945
