MINUTES LATER.

24:51.990 --> 24:54.982
YOU ARE CORRECT.
HIS GPS SHOWS HIM
HEADING TO DORCHESTER

24:55.020 --> 24:56.510
AND THEN POOF, SIGNAL DIES.

24:56.560 --> 24:58.027
ALL RIGHT.
THANKS, PENELOPE.

24:58.060 --> 25:00.528
SO MRS. SIMMONS WAS
RIGHT ABOUT HER HUSBAND
BEING ABDUCTED

25:00.560 --> 25:03.051
BUT WRONG
ABOUT CHINATOWN.

25:11.570 --> 25:13.538
UHH'
[CLANG]

25:18.650 --> 25:21.016
AAH! AAH!

25:21.050 --> 25:22.972
