25:23.020 --> 25:24.180
NO ONE CAN HEAR YOU.

25:24.220 --> 25:27.189
PLEASE, WHY ARE YOU
DOING THIS?

25:27.220 --> 25:28.881
WHO ARE YOU?

25:28.920 --> 25:30.285
WHO'S TANYA?

25:30.320 --> 25:32.720
