25:32.760 --> 25:35.126
I DON'T KNOW
WHO THAT IS.

25:35.160 --> 25:37.799
LIAR.

25:39.230 --> 25:41.767
[WHIMPERING]

25:41.800 --> 25:43.961
AAH!

25:44.010 --> 25:46.228
[SOBBING]

25:46.270 --> 25:48.636
WHO'S TANYA?

25:48.680 --> 25:51.569
[SOBBING]

25:51.610 --> 25:55.979
OK, OK, WAIT!
TANYA--TANYA IS
A WOMAN FROM WORK.

25:57.990 --> 26:00.208
IS THIS ABOUT HER?

26:00.250 --> 26:01.285
[BREATHING HARD]

26:01.320 --> 26:02.355
