26:02.390 --> 26:05.223
GOD, I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

26:05.260 --> 26:06.227
ADMIT IT.

26:06.260 --> 26:07.921
ADMIT WHAT?

26:07.960 --> 26:09.257
HOW DO YOU KNOW
HER NAME?

26:09.300 --> 26:12.326
I LOOKED. YOU CALL
AND TEXT HER A LOT.

26:12.370 --> 26:14.930
YOU'RE JUST LIKE
THE OTHERS.

26:14.970 --> 26:16.938
YOU TALK ON YOUR PHONE,

26:16.970 --> 26:19.302
AND YOU THINK YOU'RE IN
SOME KIND OF PRIVATE
LITTLE BUBBLE,

26:19.340 --> 26:20.876
BUT YOU ARE NOT.

26:20.910 --> 26:23.208
