26:32.720 --> 26:35.109
I SWEAR.

26:35.160 --> 26:37.788
MORE...

26:37.830 --> 26:40.048
LIES.

26:40.090 --> 26:41.819
NO, NO.

26:41.860 --> 26:43.157
NO, NO, NO, NO--

26:43.200 --> 26:46.192
AAH!

26:52.770 --> 26:54.169
ALL RIGHT,
THANK YOU SO MUCH. BYE.

26:54.210 --> 26:55.336
DID YOU FIND OUT?

26:55.380 --> 26:56.301
