CLASSMATE SAID

26:56.340 --> 26:58.001
THAT THEY THEY WERE TRYING
TO BUY AN ANSWER KEY

26:58.050 --> 26:59.642
TO AN UPCOMING CHEMISTRY
MIDTERM.

26:59.680 --> 27:02.342
DENISE WAGNER
WAS ON THE PHONE
WITH A CANADIAN BANKER

27:02.380 --> 27:04.985
