SET UP AN OFFSHORE ACCOUNT

27:05.020 --> 27:06.942
IN, UH, VANUATU?

27:06.990 --> 27:08.355
THE REPUBLIC
OF VANUATU.

27:08.390 --> 27:10.210
IT'S A TAX HAVEN
KNOWN FOR
ITS BANKING SECRECY.

27:10.260 --> 27:12.057
IT APPEARS SHE'D BEEN
SIPHONING OFF MONEY

27:12.090 --> 27:13.387
FROM HER CLIENTS FOR YEARS.

27:13.430 --> 27:14.556
WHAT ABOUT AMY GIBB?

27:14.600 --> 27:17.194
THE LAST PERSON
TO TALK TO AMY GIBB
WAS HER BEST FRIEND.

27:17.230 --> 27:18.367
SHE SAID THAT AMY
INVITED HER OVER

27:18.400 --> 27:20.732
TO DRINK A BOTTLE
OF CHAMPAGNE THAT
SHE STOLE FROM WORK.

27:20.770 --> 27:21.964
AND ANTHONY SIMMONS?

27:22.000 --> 27:24.309
HE LAST TALKED
TO A CURTIS PRICE,

27:24.340 --> 27:26.365
BUT HE HASN'T GOTTEN
BACK TO US YET.

27:26.410 --> 27:28.378
WHAT IF THE UNSUB KNEW ABOUT
WHAT HE CONSIDERED TO BE

27:28.410 --> 27:30.901
HIS VICTIMS' MORAL
TRANSGRESSIONS AND
HE WAS OFFENDED BY THEM?

27:30.950 --> 27:32.178
