27:32.210 --> 27:33.871
WELL, YOU KNOW HOW PEOPLE
SPILL THEIR SECRETS

27:33.920 --> 27:36.241
TO BARTENDERS,
HAI RDRESSERS,

27:36.280 --> 27:38.339
THE STRANGER SITTING
NEXT TO THEM ON A PLANE.

27:38.390 --> 27:41.917
WHEN OUR PERSONAL SPACE
IS LIMITED, IT CAN TRIGGER
A FALSE SENSE OF INTIMACY.

27:41.960 --> 27:45.225
WELL, THE BACKSEAT
OF A TAXICAB IS Ol-TEN
LIKE A CONFESSIONAL.

27:45.260 --> 27:47.751
