I DIDN'T HAVE SEX WITH TANYA.

28:14.490 --> 28:15.912
I WAS JUST JOKING, YOU KNOW?

28:15.960 --> 28:18.451
JUST GUY STUFF.

28:18.490 --> 28:20.720
