28:42.350 --> 28:46.013
THAT'S WHAT THE GUILTY
ALWAYS SAY.

28:46.050 --> 28:47.779
BUT I CAN PROVE IT.

28:49.260 --> 28:51.524
JUST LET ME CALL
A BUDDY OF MINE.

28:51.560 --> 28:54.097
DO YOU THINK I'M STUPID?!

28:54.130 --> 28:55.825
NO.

28:55.860 --> 28:57.350
