29:19.290 --> 29:21.281
LET'S CALL TANYA.

29:30.600 --> 29:31.794
THANKS FOR COMING IN,
MR. PRICE.

29:31.830 --> 29:35.539
SO YOU THINK MY
PHONE CALL WITH ANTHONY
COULD BE IMPORTANT?

29:35.570 --> 29:38.937
