HOOKED UP WITH SOME WOMAN.

29:49.480 --> 29:52.313
I ASSUME HE WASN'T TALKING
ABOUT HIS WIFE.

29:52.350 --> 29:53.988
HE GIVE YOU A NAME?

29:54.020 --> 29:55.282
NOPE.

29:55.320 --> 29:57.459
YOU SAID "CLAIMED."

29:57.490 --> 29:58.889
YOU DON'T THINK HE WAS
TELLING THE TRUTH?

29:58.930 --> 30:01.592
ADDICT S ARE GOOD AT LYING,
AGENT ROSSI.

30:01.630 --> 30:03.518
