HE'D BEEN DRINKING.

30:16.210 --> 30:19.475
I WARNED HIM THAT AN AFFAIR
COULD INTERFERE
WITH HIS SOBRIETY.

30:19.510 --> 30:21.216
I ASKED HIM TO GO
TO A MEETING WITH ME,

30:21.250 --> 30:22.342
THAT I'D EVEN DRIVE US THERE.

30:22.380 --> 30:26.942
BUT HE ENDED THE CALL,
SO I ASSUMED
THAT WAS MY ANSWER.

30:26.990 --> 30:31.620
[CELL PHONE LINE RINGING]

30:31.660 --> 30:33.184
IF YOU TRY TO WARN HER...

30:33.230 --> 30:34.595
I WON'T, I SWEAR.

30:34.630 --> 30:37.292
[VOICEMAIL] THIS IS TANYA
BENTON IN CLIENT SERVICES.

30:37.330 --> 30:38.866
PLEASE LEAVE YOUR NAME
AND NUMBER

30:38.900 --> 30:40.367
AND I'LL GET BACK
TO YOU AS SOON AS I CAN.

30:40.400 --> 30:41.367
[BEEP]

30:41.400 --> 30:43.061
THIS IS TOO BAD
FOR YOU.

30:43.100 --> 30:45.967
SHE DIDN'T RECOGNIZE
THE NUMBER.
SHE'LL CALL BACK.

30:46.010 --> 30:49.036
PLEASE, PLEASE JUST GIVE HER
SOME MORE TIME.

30:49.080 --> 30:50.877
I'M TELLING THE TRUTH.

30:50.910 --> 30:51.877
LIAR!

30:51.910 --> 30:54.276
