30:54.320 --> 30:55.617
Boy: PLEASE DON'T.
I'M NOT LYING.

30:55.650 --> 30:56.617
I'M TELLING THE TRUTH!

30:56.650 --> 30:57.617
Man: LIAR.

30:57.650 --> 30:59.413
PLEASE DON'T.

30:59.450 --> 31:01.259
[CRACK]

31:08.160 --> 31:09.559
SHE'S GOT 10 MINUTES.

31:13.130 --> 31:14.939
SIMMONS' BODY HAS YET
TO TURN UP,

31:14.970 --> 31:16.232
SO HE MAY STILL BE ALIVE,

31:16.270 --> 31:17.532
BUT WE'RE
RUNNING OUT OF TIME.

31:17.570 --> 31:19.561
THE DISPOSAL SITES
ARE ALL OVER THE MAP,

31:19.610 --> 31:21.077
BUT THE VICTIMS
WERE ALL ABDUCT ED

31:21.110 --> 31:23.431
IN THE SAME 20-BLOCK AREA
IN SOUTHIE.

31:23.480 --> 31:25.471
YEAH, BUT GARCIA'S
CHECKED AND THERE ARE
NO CURRENT RIDE-SHARE

31:25.510 --> 31:28.377
DRIVERS OR REJECTED
APPLICANTS LIVING WITHIN
THAT 20-BLOCK RADIUS.

31:28.420 --> 31:30.513
IF THE UNSUB'S OFFENDED
BY IMMORALITY, IT MIGHT
HAVE SOMETHING TO DO WITH

31:30.550 --> 31:32.916
A CHURCH OR RELIGIOUS
INSTITUTION
IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

31:32.950 --> 31:35.350
IT COULD BE A FORMER PRIEST
OR MEMBER OF THE CLERGY.

31:35.390 --> 31:37.085
RELIGION AND BRUISED KNUCKLES.

31:37.120 --> 31:39.224
