31:51.140 --> 31:52.698
4 PRIVATE,
AND ONE PAROCHIAL SCHOOL.

31:52.740 --> 31:55.629
AND CHECK FOR SCANDALS
AT THOSE SCHOOLS
AND GO BACK 30 YEARS.

31:55.680 --> 31:58.478
