32:01.080 --> 32:03.116
AND SO DO YOU.

32:06.520 --> 32:07.487
[BEEP]

32:07.520 --> 32:09.112
OH.

32:09.160 --> 32:12.084
THAT IS NOT GOOD.

32:12.130 --> 32:13.688
