32:13.730 --> 32:15.721
A PRINCIPAL AT A PRIVATE SCHOOL

32:15.760 --> 32:18.228
IN SOUTHIE WAS ARRESTED
LAST MONTH

32:18.270 --> 32:22.695
FOR SEXUALLY ASSAULTING
A MINOR. I JUST SENT YOU
THE STORY.

32:22.740 --> 32:25.538
"PRINCIPAL BRENDAN BURKE
OF ALDREN ACADEMY
WAS CHARGED WITH

32:25.570 --> 32:28.733
"LEWD ACTS AND SEXUALLY
ABUSING A 10-YEAR-OLD
FEMALE STUDENT.

32:28.780 --> 32:31.078
"POLICE BELIEVE
THERE MAY BE MORE
UNDERAGE VICTIMS

32:31.110 --> 32:33.249
DATING BACK AS EARLY
AS THE 19805."

