ALDREN IS RIGHT IN THE MIDDLE
OF THE UNSUB'S HUNTING GROUNDS.

32:35.450 --> 32:37.315
BURKE HAD BEEN PRINCIPAL
FOR 35 YEARS AND WAS KNOWN

32:37.350 --> 32:38.612
