TO DETER CRIME.

32:43.760 --> 32:44.681
OH, DEAR.

32:44.730 --> 32:45.822
WHAT IS IT, MAMA?

32:45.860 --> 32:48.499
WELL, ACCORDING TO THIS,
WHICH I'M SENDING YOU RIGHT NOW,

32:48.530 --> 32:50.748
PRINCIPAL BURKE
COMMITTED SUICIDE 10 DAYS AGO.

32:50.800 --> 32:52.665
THAT'S RIGHT WHEN
THE FIRST VICTIM WAS FOUND.

32:52.700 --> 32:53.724
