A NOTE APOLOGIZING
FOR WHAT HE CALLED

32:56.470 --> 32:58.768
HIS "SINS OF THE FLESH
AND MORAL WEAKNESS."

32:58.810 --> 33:01.335
IF THE UNSUB WENT TO ALDREN
ACADEMY, IT'S LIKELY
HE WAS INFLUENCED

33:01.380 --> 33:02.631
BY BURKE'S
MORAL CRUSADER RHETORIC.

33:02.680 --> 33:04.375
HE COULD BE TRYING
TO EMULATE HIM.

33:04.410 --> 33:06.173
GARCIA, CROSS-CHECK
THE SCHOOL'S
EN ROLLM ENT RECORDS

33:06.210 --> 33:07.677
WITH RIDE-SHARE DRIVERS
IN BOSTON.

33:07.710 --> 33:09.348
UH...NOTHING.

33:09.380 --> 33:11.109
ALL RIGHT. CHECK FOR DRIVERS
WHO'VE BEEN SUSPENDED

33:11.150 --> 33:12.640
OR HAD THEIR ACCOUNTS
DEACTIVATED.

33:12.690 --> 33:16.353
BINGO. TWO NAMES.
STEPHEN LIASTRO
AND JAMES O'NEILL.

33:16.390 --> 33:19.029
THEY BOTH WENT TO ALDREN
FROM KINDERGARTEN ALL
THE WAY THROUGH HIGH SCHOOL,

33:19.060 --> 33:20.357
STARTING IN THE EARLY EIGHTIES.

33:20.390 --> 33:22.529
STEPHEN MOVED TO CALIFORNIA
3 YEARS AGO.

33:22.560 --> 33:24.699
