33:24.730 --> 33:26.789
HE WAS A ZIMMER DRIVER
FOR 6 MONTHS.

33:30.840 --> 33:33.365
INCLUDING AN ALLEGATION
THAT HE THREATENED A PASSENGER

33:33.410 --> 33:35.230
WITH A HAMMER.
BUT CHARGES WEREN'T FILED.

33:35.280 --> 33:36.679
THAT'S WHY HE DIDN'T
SHOW UP ON THE DATABASE

33:36.710 --> 33:37.506
OF DRIVERS
WITH CRIMINAL HISTORIES.

33:37.540 --> 33:39.474
LET'S PUT OUT AN APB
FOR JAMES O'NEILL.

33:39.510 --> 33:42.047
ALREADY SENT.
WE NEED THE HOME ADDRESS,
GARCIA.

33:42.080 --> 33:45.049
GOD...

33:45.090 --> 33:48.753
GRANT ME THE SERENITY
TO ACCEPT THE THINGS
THAT I CANNOT CHANGE,

33:48.790 --> 33:53.056
THE COURAGE TO CHANGE
THE THINGS THAT I CAN...

33:53.090 --> 33:55.752
AND THE WISDOM
TO KNOW THE DIFFERENCE.

33:57.730 --> 34:00.563
THE SERENITY PRAYER.

34:10.110 --> 34:11.270
YOU'RE ALL SINNERS.

34:11.310 --> 34:14.143
AND SINNERS MUST BE PUNISHED.

34:14.180 --> 34:15.613
STAND UP STRAIGHT!

34:15.650 --> 34:17.117
PUT OUT YOUR HANDS!

34:17.150 --> 34:18.117
[SMACKING, BOYS CRYING OUT]

34:18.150 --> 34:20.539
PLEASE DON'T. NO MORE.

34:20.590 --> 34:22.080
I'M TELLING THE TRUTH!

34:22.120 --> 34:25.089
LIAR! LIAR! LIAR!

34:34.870 --> 34:39.204
DO YOU KNOW WHAT THAT
SELF-RIGHTEOUS
SON OF A BITCH DID?

34:41.210 --> 34:45.101
HE MOLESTED LITTLE GIRLS.

34:45.150 --> 34:46.742
BUT HE'S NOT GONNA BE PUNISHED!

34:46.780 --> 34:49.112
HE TOOK THE EASY WAY OUT.

34:49.150 --> 34:53.211
HE LEI-T A PATHETIC NOTE.

34:53.250 --> 34:55.855
IT IS NOT...

34:55.890 --> 34:57.380
FAIR!

34:57.420 --> 35:00.526
SINNERS MUST BE PUNISHED!

35:00.560 --> 35:02.755
SINNERS LIKE YOU!

35:02.800 --> 35:04.768
YOUR TIME'S UP.

35:04.800 --> 35:07.360
NO! OHH...

35:07.400 --> 35:09.129
[CELL PHONE RINGING]

35:12.570 --> 35:13.559
[RINGING CONTINUES]

35:18.950 --> 35:23.410
[CELL PHONE RINGING]

35:26.820 --> 35:28.811
HELLO, TANYA.

35:28.860 --> 35:32.455
TANYA, I'M--[CLEARS THROAT]

35:32.490 --> 35:35.527
INVESTIGATING
THE ANTHONY SIMMONS CASE.

35:35.560 --> 35:39.599
YES, IT IS TERRIBLE.

35:39.630 --> 35:41.837
HOW DO YOU KNOW MR. SIMMONS?

35:43.670 --> 35:46.833
