35:52.480 --> 35:56.416
THANK YOU.
YOU HAVE BEEN A BIG HELP.

35:56.450 --> 36:00.341
I THINK THAT HE'LL BE FOUND
VERY SOON, TOO.

36:01.890 --> 36:05.189
FOR YEARS JAMES O'NEILL
AND THE OTHER STUDENTS
AT ALDREN ACADEMY

36:05.230 --> 36:07.323
FELT THE RIGHTEOUS WRATH
OF PRINCIPAL BURKE.

36:07.360 --> 36:09.499
I DON'T KNOW WHY
THEIR PARENTS
DIDN'T COMPLAIN

36:09.530 --> 36:10.827
OR PUT A STOP TO BURKE.

36:10.860 --> 36:13.829
SOME PARENTS WOULD RATHER
HAVE SOMEONE ELSE
DISCIPLINE THEIR KIDS.

36:13.870 --> 36:16.293
BROKEN HANDS, CONTUSIONS,
CONCUSSIONS--

36:16.340 --> 36:17.830
THAT'S NOT DISCIPLINE,
THAT'S ABUSE.

36:17.870 --> 36:19.167
JAMES WAS ANGERED
BY BURKE'S HYPOCRISY,

36:19.210 --> 36:22.338
AND WHEN BURKE TOOK
HIS OWN LIFE, IT DENIED
JAMES THE SATISFACTION

36:22.380 --> 36:24.746
OF SEEING HIM PUBLICLY
HUMILIATED AND PUNISHED.

36:24.780 --> 36:28.910
SO HE FELT COMPELLED
TO PUNISH OTHERS
HE DEEMED IMMORAL.

36:35.560 --> 36:37.915
I CONFESS.

36:37.960 --> 36:40.952
IS THAT WHAT YOU WANT TO HEAR?

36:40.990 --> 36:41.957
YOU'RE RIGHT.

36:42.000 --> 36:43.399
I'M A SINNER.

36:43.430 --> 36:45.728
I MADE A MISTAKE.

36:45.770 --> 36:49.331
BUT IT'LL NEVER HAPPEN AGAIN.

36:49.370 --> 36:51.235
PLEASE...

36:51.270 --> 36:53.261
I DON'T WANT TO DIE.

36:53.310 --> 36:55.471
IT'S TOO LATE.

36:58.040 --> 37:00.474
IT'S TIME FOR YOU
TO JOIN THE OTHERS.

37:01.750 --> 37:03.308
OTH ERS?

37:06.290 --> 37:09.316
HE HAD A WALL OF SHAME.

37:12.290 --> 37:14.019
SO DO I.

37:14.060 --> 37:16.551
OH, MY GOD!

37:16.600 --> 37:18.864
SOMEBODY HELP ME!

37:18.900 --> 37:20.959
JAMES O'NEILL, FBI!

37:22.740 --> 37:23.695
STAY AWAY!

37:23.740 --> 37:25.002
WE'RE COMING IN!

37:25.040 --> 37:28.430
ONE STEP AND I'LL DROP IT.

37:28.480 --> 37:29.230
[WHIMPERING]

37:29.280 --> 37:31.840
Morgan: TAKE IT EASY.
TAKE IT EASY.

37:33.650 --> 37:34.912
HOTCH.

37:36.420 --> 37:38.047
YOU NEED TO RELEASE HIM, JAMES.

37:38.080 --> 37:39.911
NO. HE'S A CHEATER.

37:39.950 --> 37:41.281
DON'T LET HIM KILL ME.

37:41.320 --> 37:42.810
HOLD ON, MR. SIMMONS.

37:42.860 --> 37:44.384
WE KNOW WHAT BRENDAN BURKE
DID TO YOU.

37:44.430 --> 37:45.385
HE'S A LIAR.

37:45.430 --> 37:47.990
HE'S A HYPOCRITE.

37:48.030 --> 37:50.419
HE'S...HE'S A PERVERT.

37:50.460 --> 37:54.863
YES. AND SOON THE WORLD
WILL KNOW THE TRUTH
ABOUT WHAT A MONSTER HE WAS.

37:54.900 --> 37:58.438
BUT HE'LL NEVER
BE PUNISHED.

37:58.470 --> 38:00.404
YOU HURTING OTHER PEOPLE
IS NOT GONNA CHANGE THAT.

38:00.440 --> 38:01.532
AND WE DON'T WANT
TO HURT YOU.

38:01.580 --> 38:03.036
GET ME OUT OF THIS THING!

38:03.080 --> 38:04.809
SHUT UP!

38:04.850 --> 38:06.943
AAH!

38:06.980 --> 38:09.471
[SOBBING]

38:21.130 --> 38:24.964
Hotch: "A MAN'S
VERY HIGHEST MOMENT IS,
I HAVE NO DOUBT AT ALL,

38:25.000 --> 38:27.719
"WHEN HE KNEELS IN THE DUST
AND BEATS HIS BREAST

38:27.770 --> 38:30.091
AND TELLS ALL THE SINS
OF HIS LIFE."

38:30.140 --> 38:32.404
OSCAR WILDE.

38:43.680 --> 38:47.411
[CAR APPROACH ES]

38:51.790 --> 38:52.757
TARA.

38:52.790 --> 38:53.825
HEY THERE.

38:53.860 --> 38:55.748
THIS IS A NICE SURPRISE.

38:55.800 --> 38:57.995
YEAH. YOU NEED A HAND?

38:58.030 --> 39:00.464
SURE. GRAB A RAG.

39:00.500 --> 39:02.138
[LAUGHS] OK. BEFORE THAT,

39:02.170 --> 39:03.660
I COME BEARING GII-TS.

39:03.700 --> 39:07.431
COFFEE AND THIS.

39:10.180 --> 39:12.876
AN ORIGINAL RADIO
ANTENNA KNOB.

39:12.910 --> 39:13.842
YOU FOUND ONE.

39:13.880 --> 39:16.644
YEAH. YOU JUST HAVE TO KNOW
THE RIGHT PEOPLE.

39:19.420 --> 39:21.752
IT FITS PERFECT.
THANK YOU.

39:21.790 --> 39:23.417
AND YOUR DAD.

39:23.460 --> 39:24.484
I WILL TELL HIM.

39:24.530 --> 39:26.521
[CAR STARTS,
ENGINE HUMS]

39:26.560 --> 39:27.527
YOU HEAR THAT?

39:27.560 --> 39:29.027
SHE SOUNDS INCREDIBLE.

39:29.060 --> 39:32.029
THAT'S THE SOUND
OF THE OPEN ROAD
CALLING US.

39:32.070 --> 39:34.561
NOW YOU ARE TALKING,
MY FRIEND.

39:36.940 --> 39:40.068
* FLY ME TO THE MOON

39:40.110 --> 39:44.877
* LET ME PLAY
AMONG THE STARS *

39:44.910 --> 39:48.539
* LET ME SEE WHAT
SPRING IS LIKE *

39:48.580 --> 39:52.914
* ON JUPITER AND MARS

39:52.950 --> 39:56.181
* IN OTHER WORDS

39:56.220 --> 39:58.427
* HOLD MY HAND
